      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, approved\n\nOleg, please consider landing this to master, to avoid conflicts with other patches under development.  I'd be happy if all features using OBD_CONNECT flags would do the same, since we've had several cases of features that almost landed on b1_8 and master with different OBD_CONNECT values.",
